Photo by Nomninjas on May 04, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'of room temp boiled AIYU JELLY Instructions: Prepare 3000 water mineral water 2. Pour 38g of Aiyu seed into the cloth bag OR filter bag 3. Soak the cloth bag with the seed into the prepared bowl of water for about 10mins Rub in the bowl of water for the about 6 to 10 min. (can stop when there are no jelly like substance when squeeze the bag of aiyu seed) 5. The clear water would become golden and jelly would form after 40 to 60 mins.'

Photo by Nomninjas on May 04, 2020. Image may contain: text that says '5. The clear water would become golden and jelly would form after 40 to 60 mins. (Recommended to refrigerate it) 6. Add in the lemon juice, coconut syrup or honey to serve cold OR any of your own recipe. *its natural forming jelly without gelatos min or artificial ingredients hence highly recommended to consume within the day as 40-50% will turn back to liquid form after a day*'
